<chapter id="hdbk-bars"><title>Main toolbar and menubar</title>
<para></para>

<section id="hdbk-bars-toolbar"><title>Toolbar</title>
<section id="hdbk-bars-toolbar-config"><title>Configuration</title>
<para>
The main window toolbar is configurable.  Access this with the "Configure
tool bars" entry under the "Settings" menubar entry.

<mediaobject>
<imageobject>
<imagedata  fileref="hdbk-bars-toolbar-Configtoolbar.png" format="png"/>
</imageobject>
<textobject>
<phrase>Toolbar Configuration Dialog Box</phrase>
</textobject>
</mediaobject>
</para>

<para> Each of the buttons has tooltips to tell what their function is.
For buttons with no pixmap, the buttons could appear as blank, or just blank bars.
</para>
</section>
