<section id="hdbk-bars-menubar"><title>Menubar</title>
<para></para>

<section id="hdbk-bars-menubar-file"><title>File</title>
<para>

<variablelist>
<varlistentry>
<term>New window</term>
<listitem>
<para>opens another instance of Bibletime</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>Close</term>
<listitem>
<para>closes the presenter that has focus</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>Quit</term>
<listitem>
<para>Quits Bibletime</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

</variablelist>
</para>
</section>

<section id="hdbk-bars-menubar-Window"><title>Window</title>
<para>
<variablelist>

<varlistentry>
<term>Cascade</term>
<listitem><para>Cascades open presenters</para></listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>Tile</term>
<listitem>
<para>Tiles open presenters</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>Auto Cascade</term>
<listitem>
<para>
Automatically cascades newly opened presenters
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>Auto Tile</term>
<listitem>
<para>ditto for tiling newly opened presenters</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>Close all</term>
<listitem>
<para>Closes all open presenters</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>List of open modules</term>
<listitem>
<para>Do I have to explain?</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

</variablelist>
</para>
</section>

<section id="hdbk-bars-menubar-settings"><title>Settings</title>
<para>

<variablelist>
<varlistentry>
<term>Show Toolbar</term>
<listitem>
<para>Show or hide the main toolbar, normally shown</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>Configure Toolbar</term>
<listitem>
<para>show the Configure Toolbar dialog</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>Preferences</term>
<listitem>
<para>show the Preferences dialog</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>Show Strongs</term>
<listitem>
<para>
display Strong's number in the text (only certain modules use this
function)
</para> </listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>Show Footnotes</term>
<listitem>
<para>
display footnotes in the text (only certain modules use this function)
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>Show Main Index</term>
<listitem>
<para>
show or hide the module list window. Normally it is not hidden, unless you want
maximum real estate for displaying modules. BTW, resizing the Main Index
window can accomplish the same thing, although to a lesser extent.
</para>
</listitem> </varlistentry>
</variablelist>

</para>
</section>

<section id="hdbk-bars-menubar-Help"><title>Help</title>
<para>

<variablelist>

<varlistentry>
<term>Contents</term>
<listitem><para>
Opens KDE's help browser with Bibletime's handbook
</para></listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>What's This</term>
<listitem>
<para>
allows you to click on certain items for contextual help
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>Bug Report</term>
<listitem>
<para>
send a bug report to the program's maintainers to help development
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>About Bibletime</term>
<listitem>
<para>
opens a window with general Bibletime information
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry>
<term>About KDE</term>
<listitem>
<para>
opens a window with general KDE information
</para>
</listitem>

</varlistentry>

</variablelist>

</para>
</section>

</section>
<section id="hdbk-term-hotkeys"><title>Hotkeys</title>
<para>
All of the hotkeys listed here can be changed in the Options Dialog.
</para>
<table>
<title>Default Hotkeys</title>
<tgroup cols="2">
<thead>
<row>
<entry>Action</entry>
 <entry>Default Hotkey</entry>
</row>
</thead>

<tbody>
<row>
<entry>Auto Tile</entry><entry>Ctrl+Alt+T</entry></row>
<row><entry>Auto Cascade </entry><entry>Ctrl+Alt+A </entry></row>
<row><entry>Cascade </entry><entry>Ctrl+A </entry></row>
<row><entry>Close All </entry><entry>Shift+Ctrl+A</entry></row>
<row><entry>Configure Toolbars</entry><entry></entry></row>
<row><entry>Preferences </entry><entry></entry></row>
<row><entry>Quit </entry><entry>Ctrl+Q</entry></row>
<row><entry>Remove Selected Item(s)</entry><entry>Ctrl+Alt+D</entry></row>
<row><entry>Reset Main Index </entry><entry>Ctrl+Alt+R</entry></row>
<row><entry>Search in Selected Module(s) </entry><entry>Ctrl+Alt+S</entry></row>
<row><entry>Show Strongs</entry><entry>Ctrl+Alt+S</entry></row>
<row><entry>Show Footnotes </entry><entry>Ctrl+Alt+F</entry></row>
<row><entry>Tile </entry><entry>Ctrl+T </entry></row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</section>

